{"tid":2283761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國民謠改詞] 《榮光歸我家這裡》","createTime":"2020-11-12T22:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T09:59:00.000Z","uid":154486,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9409eb52aad143a144db400cb19fd2c12f0c61","tid":2283761,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T22:01:57.000Z","msg":"近牌好多人諗緊走唔走，諗緊趁大家仲係度，想改下歌仔比大家唱下<br />\n最近睇到美國人唱呢首God Bless America，幾感動就改下詞睇下大家鐘唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\n留意個「榮」字要佔多個音<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x7CjEo8RMn8?t=92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx7CjEo8RMn8%3Ft%3D92&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=ece56138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x7CjEo8RMn8?t=92</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">榮光歸我家這裡 名香譽滿港<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">God bless America, land that I love</span><br />\n縱使分離 請希冀<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">Stand beside her and guide her</span><br />\n未怕黑 光滿天再耀眼<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">Through the night with the light from above</span><br />\n綠翠山巒 未見邊緣<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">From the mountains to the prairies</span><br />\n鬧市海旁 迎浪破風！<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">To the oceans white with foam</span><br />\n<br />\n榮光歸我家這裡 歸於我心！<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">God bless America, my home sweet home</span><br />\n榮光歸我家這裡 歸於香港！<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">God bless America, my home sweet</span> home<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n往後仲有幾首改緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位教友屌細力D<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8849fd5af9f67ef120ec133116a427d22aac8ea3","tid":2283761,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T22:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05c0b66916bc9aeddecb8168c0ee54a39175570e","tid":2283761,"uid":257516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc